{
  "stem": "24242.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had Gentile-- as I said, some of our Gentile people that were good people and knew my brothers, my brothers knew them well, through them, they bought.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They helped them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they got a couple of rifles or a couple of machine guns, then already was no problem.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because then they would go and see by force where to catch a policeman or a few policemen or a few Germans and take away their arms-- butcher them, kill them, and they would have arms.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is the way it started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, towards the end of '42, we had already quite a few hundred people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the way my brothers knew a certain area of people, a certain amount of Gentile, so did other Jews knew where is a wealth area, where is a poorer area.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they already knew who is on our side and who is on the German side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that's the way they would go at night and get as far as food goes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this was not the main-- this was the main problem to exist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the main problem to my brothers I guess, was at the time to repay those collaborators that gave us-- my parents-- terrorized us in the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that fellow that he told the Nazis they should arrest me-- if you remember that Polish man-- that I was arrested for a few hours.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First of all, what they did is paid them with interest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This very same fellow, that he arrested me with the Nazis in Nowogrodek in 1943.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In 1943, again, it was in the winter.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
